  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_136",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, these have learned the skills to use magic. It's still quite crude, but they use spells that can heal wounds, stop bleeding, and such. For those in the underworld who believe in superstitions and rely on spells rather than medical care, even an orc can be a lifesaver.",
